{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Wto_utils.Make</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Fixpoint","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Wto_utils","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Make","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[{"title":"Parameters","href":"#parameters","children":[]},{"title":"Signature","href":"#signature","children":[]}],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<h2 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Parameters</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec parameter anchored\" id=\"argument-1-N\"><a href=\"#argument-1-N\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> </span><span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html\">N</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../module-type-NODE/index.html\">NODE</a></span></code></div></div><h2 id=\"signature\"><a href=\"#signature\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Signature</h2><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-map\"><a href=\"#val-map\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> map : <span><span>(<span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span>bool <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <a href=\"../../Wto/index.html#type-partition\">Wto.partition</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <a href=\"../../Wto/index.html#type-partition\">Wto.partition</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>map f wto</code> applies <code>f</code> to every element of <code>wto</code> while conserving the w.t.o. structure. The second argument of <code>f</code> is <code>true</code> if the argument of <code>f</code> is a head.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-iter\"><a href=\"#val-iter\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> iter : <span><span>(<span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span>bool <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <a href=\"../../Wto/index.html#type-partition\">Wto.partition</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>iter f wto</code> applies <code>f</code> to every element of <code>wto</code>. The second argument of <code>f</code> is true if the argument of <code>f</code> is a head.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-is_head_of\"><a href=\"#val-is_head_of\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> is_head_of : <span><span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <a href=\"../../Wto/index.html#type-partition\">Wto.partition</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>head_of wto h n</code> returns whether <code>n</code> is inside the component of head <code>h</code>. <code>h</code> must be a head. Returns true also if <code>n = h</code>. Complexity: linear in the number of nodes.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-depth\"><a href=\"#val-depth\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> depth : <span><span><a href=\"argument-1-N/index.html#type-t\">N.t</a> <a href=\"../../Wto/index.html#type-partition\">Wto.partition</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Maximum number of heads among all nodes, i.e. maximum number of nested components.</p></div></div>"}